	Made macro SIM_AC_GLU_NURBSOBJECT for testing what the name of the
	GLU NURBS interface structure is.

2000-06-30 19:34  larsa

	* coin.m4:
	
	Removed coin_version variable (got sim_ac_coin_version anyway).

